column5: Good morning marc thorpe, Roy, Fisherman
Why are youse guys awake this time of the morning, going fishing?
I'm always up at this time of the day. It's the best time of the day for me. It's my quiet tme. If one day you see that I 'm not up by 4:30, call 911.
lol  should I alert the media also??????????  I had a shift change at work, gonna take me a couple of days to get used to it, and I am probably going back to bed in an hour or so
.....Oh my, seems I've slept in. Oh wait, it's Saturday I'm allowed.  Mornining folks.
Morning boys, Sitting here eating cold pizza......what to do on a rainy saturday morning....
....Rain what rain? Skies are clear and blue here Chris but I guess if you got rain we'll be getting it here later today.
Its suppose to clear up eventually this morning so you never know....Maybe some local carpin might be in order
What a bunch of lazy bums sleeping so late in the day  Hope y'all had a good one  Maureen
Ha, actually it's called the night shift, and this is the last one, 1800-0600hrs.
